From John Daker Subject Re Boom Hubcap attack In a previous article Speedy Mercer says I was attacked by a rabid hubcap I was going to work on a Yamaha Twin the vibrating tank when I heard a wierd noise off to my I caught a glimpse of something silver headed for my left foot and jerked it up about a nanosecond before my bike was hit HARD in the left When I went to put my foot back on the peg I found that it was not there I pulled into the nearest parking lot and discovered that I had been hit by a wire wheel type hubcap from a large cage This hubcap weighed about pounds The impact had bent the left peg flat against the frame and tweeked the shifter in the Had I not heard the approaching cap I feel certian that I would be sans a portion of my left wondered where that hubcap DoD DarkMan The significant problems we face cannot be solved at the same level of thinking we were at when we created Albert Einstein The Eternal Champion